77/gazebo/physics/Joint_TEST.cc?at=simbody#cl-29), it appears the two axis associations are flipped.\r\n\r\nPropose to flip them back during universal joint construction to make it consistent with the manual.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://ode-wiki.org/wiki/index.php?title=Manual:_All&amp;printable=yes#Universal\" rel=\"nofollow\">ODE manual</a>, axis 1 is attached to body 1 (parent link) and axis 2 is attached to body 2 (child link).  From <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/7d38f34f3d2704cab379b9bb0f91d86289b68f77/gazebo/physics/Joint_TEST.cc?at=simbody#cl-29\" rel=\"nofollow\">experimenting with the joint</a>, it appears the two axis associations are flipped.</p>\n<p>Propose to flip them back during universal joint construction to make it consistent with the manual.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-12-27T20:10:25.591848+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:44:45.290777+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 991}